column1: The Price Field in product filter is accepting alphabetic character
column26:
The Price Field in product filter is accepting alphabetic character

Steps To Reproduce
1.Navigate to retail website
2.Select catalog and then product
3.Enter alphabet in Price filed of filter product

Expected Result
On clicking filter it should show validation method

Actual Result
On clicking filter it is accepting the value

column1: The search feature in add image module is not workiing
column26:
The search feature while trying to upload an image is not working

Steps To Reproduce
 1. Navigate to Retail Website
 2. Select Catalog and then product
 3. Then navigate to add products and search for an image to use

Expexted Result
 If the image exists then it should show the image

Actual Result 

 Although the image exists the file is not being shown

ScreenShot
 !image-2022-02-17-12-26-15-130.png|thumbnail! 

 !image-2022-02-17-12-27-00-987.png|thumbnail!

column1: Verify the Search feature in upload image works for products module
The Add product features is allowing to upload png image
column26:
The add product feature is allowing to upload png image but it should only allow us to upload jpg image file type

Steps To Reproduce
 1.Navigate to retail website
 2. Select catalog and then select product and go to add products option
 3. upload an image other than jpg

Expected Result
 It should show an error message 

Actual Result 
 The file is being uploaded

Screenshot
   !image-2022-02-17-11-57-36-555.png|thumbnail!

column1: The mail is being sent with blank input in message field
column26:
The mail is being sent with blank input in message field 

Steps To Reproduce 
 1. Navigate to Retail Website 
 2. Select Marketing and then Select Mail Option
 3. send a mail without writing anything in the message field 

Expected Result
  On clicking send button it should should show a validation message

Actual Result
  On clicking send button the mail is being sent

ScreenShot

 !image-2022-02-16-15-37-27-950.png|thumbnail!

column1: Verify that the mail with blank input in message field
Even if the subject field is balnk the mail is being sent
column26:
Empty mail subject messages are being sent

Steps to reproduce 
 1. Navigate to Retail website
 2. Select marketing and move to mail
 3. send mail without any subject

Expected Result
  There should appear a validation message saying that subject field is empty

Actual Result
   The mail with blank subject value is being sent 

ScreenShot
 !image-2022-02-16-14-46-42-249.png|thumbnail!

column1: The Subject field is accepting more than 1000 characters
column26:
The subject field in Mail module should not allow more than 1000 characters in Text box.

Steps To Reproduce 
  1. Navigate to the retail website
  2. GO to marketing and then to Mail
  3. Enter more than 1000 characters in Subject field 

Expected Result
   On clicking send , it should show a validation message 

Actual  Result
    The mail is being sent
